(161, 1, '2013-04-01 16:05:30', '2013-04-01 16:05:30', 'Nepal, also known as the Switzerland of Asia, is not only beautiful with its snow-capped mountains, crystal-clear lakes, gushing rivers, rare variety of flora and fauna, myriad temples and stupas but equally exotic as well. It’s a Shangri-La where people come with a hope of having a glimpse of Yeti, a mysterious abominable snow animal, or even in quest for nirvana or enlightenment. But at the same time it is a country where tradition and modernity intermingle with each other and peoples with diverse languages, religions and cultures co-exist.\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_180\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"205\"]<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-180\" title=\"Little Buddha DVD Cover\" src=\"http://www.nepalfilming.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/little-buddha-DVDcover-205x300.jpg\" alt=\"Little Buddha DVD Cover\" width=\"205\" height=\"300\" /> Little Buddha DVD Cover[/caption]\n\nEvery year many documentary filmmakers come to Nepal to capture the rich cultural heritage and diversity with their cameras. Some even come just to capture the rare natural beauty and virgin locales of the land.\n\nBut even large-scale productions have been shot in Nepal. Films like The Little Buddha and The Golden Child have captured the glorious past, the diverse landscape, the rich cultural heritage and architectural splendor of the land. The Oscar-nominated Caravan, portraying fortitude of the people living amidst adverse natural conditions in Dolpo, a mountain district, has captured the majestic panorama of mountainous landscapes and lakes.\n\n<strong>The Film and Documentary Coordinated by Us:</strong>\n<strong>2006</strong> - Pakistan: Hotel (TV Serial)\n<strong>2008</strong> - Italy: Azzurra Music - Beautiful Planet\n<strong>2008</strong> - Japan (YTV) : Gutto!Chikyubin = Special deliver over the Earth\n<strong>2008</strong> - Polska: Agata and the monks\n<strong>2010</strong> - Japan TV Tokyo: Bee Museum\n<strong>2012 -</strong> CBC / TBS - The Earth\n<strong>2013</strong> - TBS TV Japan Chikyu Daikikou\n<strong>2013 -</strong> TBS - WORLD HERITAGE\n<strong>2014 - </strong>Channel NewsAsia - Days of Rage\n<strong>2014 -</strong> TELEVISION NIIGATA NETWORK - Backpacker\nand many more Etc,...\n\n<strong>A few others International movies shot in Nepal:</strong>\nHollywood: Little Buddha, The Golden Child, The Wind Horse, Red Corner\nBollywood: Hare Ram Hare Krishna, Yudh, Khuda Gawah, Ghar Wali Bahar Wali, Mahan, Love in Nepal, Ek Hasina Ek Diwana, Bekabu\nHong Kong: Bodhi Dharma, Qi Yuah\nFrance: II Fiore Delle Mille e Una Notte, Caravan\nMountain Movies: The Conquest of Everest', 'Portfolio', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'portfolio', '', '', '2013-04-01 16:05:30', '2013-04-01 16:05:30', '', 0, 'http://www.nepalfilming.com/?page_id=161', 0, 'page', '', 0),
