of locations freedom to filmmakers planning filming in Nepal!\r\n\r\nLiberty Films provide full line coordinator services with divisions devoted to the production, post production, distribution of theatrical motion pictures as well as home entertainment, television, music, theater. Serving the entertainment world for over a decade, we have provided our services for several production houses, feature films, corporate films and several music videos. We have dedicated team of Cinematographers, Film Directors, Executive Producers, Camera Man, Crews, Artists and Location Managers. We have not only coordinate professional assignments for our clients in Nepal but also executed several International projects. We offer wide range of services to facilitate an affordable production with highest professional standards. We provide productions with a full package of services from research to coordination, filming and post production.\r\n\r\nWe will work together to get your movie made within your budget, Contact us with your concept or screenplay.\r\nThank you.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-8\" src=\"http://libertyfilms.com.np/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/our_team_president.jpg\" alt=\"our_team_president\" width=\"200\" height=\"241\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Mr. Ghale Ram</strong>\r\n\r\nDirector | Producer | Actor\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://ghalegroup.com\" target=\"_blank\">Ghale Treks  </a> - (Since 2000 Year)\r\n<a href=\"http://libertyholidays.com\" target=\"_blank\">Liberty Holidays </a> - ( Since 2010 Year)\r\n<a href=\"http://helpyouhelp.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Creative Hands </a>– ( Since 2007 Year)\r\n<a href=\"http://www.nepalfilming.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Liberty Films Pvt. Ltd.</a>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '882-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-17 14:06:37', '2015-06-17 08:21:37', '', 882, 'http://libertyfilms.com.np/882-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
