(994, 1, '2015-07-14 09:54:24', '2015-07-14 09:54:24', 'We arrange all kinds of filming shoot in Nepal. Our rapport with bureaucracy &amp; knowledge of rules &amp; regulations enable us to smoothly obtain all kinds of filming permits to shoot at the locations of your choice! As per your budget we can arrange vehicles, accommodations be it luxurious or heritage hotels or budget stay. Travelling by air or overland can be arranged. Nepal itself is highest producer of films thus there is easy availability of all the facilities required for shooting. Small/big studios, labs, post -production assistance, skilled helping crew, etc. are all obtainable in Nepal. In this way Our Team at Liberty Holidays is capable in providing both material and human resources needed for shooting a film.\r\n\r\nWe are coordinating total production service provider for following!\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Location Scouting</li>\r\n	<li>Films, movie</li>\r\n	<li>TV Commercials</li>\r\n	<li>Music Videos</li>\r\n	<li>Television Series</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate films</li>\r\n	<li>Documentary production</li>\r\n	<li>Live Event Coverage</li>\r\n	<li>News agency, productions</li>\r\n	<li>Fashion &amp; Product Photography</li>\r\n	<li>Research Services</li>\r\n	<li>Transportation</li>\r\n	<li>Hotel and Travel Services</li>\r\n	<li>Permits and Necessary authorization paper works</li>\r\n	<li>Artists arrangements</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>Low cost of production</strong>\r\n\r\nThe best part about filming in Nepal is the cost of total production which is comparably lower than any other location. It is so due to the vast network of facilities presented in country. Whether it is specified filming related expenses or general expenses such as accommodation, movement from one location to other, etc. Nepal offers excellent range of facilities at competitive rates.\r\n\r\n<strong>Easy Communication</strong>\r\n\r\nApart from the above-mentioned major facilities there are other  benefits also like easy  communication with local people. As English is one of the official languages and widely spoken in every part of country. This makes it easier for international crew members to communicate with local crew members. If the foreign crew belongs to non-English speaking country then also local guides or interpreters can hire by us!', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-14 09:54:24', '2015-07-14 09:54:24', '', 10, 'http://win-server:8080/pasang/libertyflims/uncategorized/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
