(1555, 1, '2015-01-27 18:00:25', '2015-01-27 18:00:25', '<em><strong>Name :  Angela Shrestha\r\n</strong></em><strong><em> Address : Chhauni, Kathmandu, Nepal</em></strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/angilashrestha.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1154\" src=\"http://pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/angilashrestha-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"angilashrestha\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Own words:\r\n</strong>I would like to thanks Ojash Lama for letting me know such wonderful program. I m feeling really good after completing this new song \"Timi Mero ho\" which is composed and lyrics by Ojash lama. I also would like to thanks Adapters band. Well, I was very nervous on video shooting but I really enjoyed.\r\n\r\nThank you  PMST Nepal and entire time for letting me a chance.\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/3gQDzTgEu0A\r\n\r\n<em>Timi Mero Ho - Angela Shrestha (Official Music Video)</em>\r\n<em>PMST Nepal (1st Chance)</em>\r\n<em>Lyrics - Ojash Lama</em>\r\n<em>Compose : Adapters</em>\r\n<em>Model - Lalit Ghale, Chinese Dai (Teacher)</em>\r\n<em>Music - PMST Nepal</em>\r\n<em>Editor - Pema Man Singh Tamang</em>\r\n<em>Camera/Director - Sagun Lama</em>', 'Angela Shrestha', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'angela-shrestha', '', '', '2015-12-31 12:26:34', '2015-12-31 12:26:34', '', 0, 'http://pmstnepal.com/new/?post_type=1st_chance&#038;p=1555', 0, '1st_chance', '', 0),
(1556, 1, '2015-02-20 18:28:16', '2015-02-20 18:28:16', '<em><strong>Name :  Kailash Bhusal\r\n</strong></em><em><strong> Address : Bhaktapur, Nepal</strong></em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Own words:\r\n</strong>I live in Bhaktapur. From my childhood I grew up within the musical environment. I have participant in many cultural program and preform many places in Kathmandu. Many times I release for to recording my own song but due to many reason I was unsuccessful. After knowing this project, I finally step in and had my not only the recorded song I also have my own video. I m vary glad to participant on this project because I almost lost my hope.\r\n\r\nThank you PMST Nepal and the entire team for such wonderful opportunity.\r\n\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KNqlvd5yvPQ\" width=\"100%\" height=\"392\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><span data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span></iframe>\r\n\r\n<em>Pida Haru - Kailash Bhusal (Official Music Video)</em>\r\n<em>PMST Nepal (1st Chance)</em>\r\n<em>Lyrics/Compose - Suraj Yonjan</em>\r\n<em>Music - PMST Nepal</em>\r\n<em>Editor - Pema Man Singh Tamang</em>\r\n<em>Camera/Director - Sagun Lama</em>', 'Kailash Bhusal', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kailash-bhusal', '', '', '2018-12-23 20:26:35', '2018-12-23 14:41:35', '', 0, 'http://pmstnepal.com/new/?post_type=1st_chance&#038;p=1556', 0, '1st_chance', '', 0),
