(3335, 1, '2018-09-28 11:35:33', '2018-09-28 05:50:33', 'A historical movie “Nalapani”s trailer is out on YouTube.The teaser of \'Nalapani\' has been made in the historical story. Teaser of the film has been published by Padma Kumari films PVT.LTD.  a program in the Kathmandu on Thursday.\r\n\r\nNalapani is the place where Nepali Army defeated British East India Company. This film is presented by Padma Kumari films PVT.LTD. in association with Ganga Narayan Films Production PVT. LTD. Nepal.\r\n\r\nArjun Jung Shahi, Santosh Pant, Desh Bhakta Khanal, Poozana Pradhan, Manoj Shakya, Janak Bataula, sushil Khadka, Hikmat Thapaliya, Geeta Adhikari, Geeta Bista and many other artist starrer historic films “Nalapani” is directed by Ramesh Adhikari. Ghanendra Thapaliya is executive producer and Manoj Shakya is the producer of this film. Film is scripted by Ramesh Adhikari, Krishna Acharya.\r\n\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kNssnlTkXyo\" width=\"100%\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>', 'Historical movie “Nalapani”s trailer is released out on YouTube.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'historical-movie-nalapanis-trailer-is-released-out-on-youtube', '', '', '2018-09-28 12:16:01', '2018-09-28 06:31:01', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=3335', 0, 'post', '', 0),
