(1690, 1, '2016-01-01 04:12:26', '2016-01-01 04:12:26', '<a href=\"http://localhost/projects/pmstnepal/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Rai-dai.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1957\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1957\" src=\"http://localhost/projects/pmstnepal/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Rai-dai.jpg\" alt=\"Rai dai\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Om K. Rai\r\n</strong>Coordinator<strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Adddress : Changunarayan -3 KTM (Jhapa)\r\n</strong><strong>DOB : 1979-10-23\r\nMarital Status : Married </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Eductaion\r\n</strong>BA Passed (Secular Field)\r\nMaster Of Theology Passed (Theological Field)\r\n\r\n<strong>Experience &amp;Trainings\r\n</strong>Teaching in a Boarding School\r\nTraining of Psychology (3yrs)Training of \" How to make Flim\" With the Great Nepali Director Mr. Tulashi Ghimire\r\nParticipant Asian Access (3yrs) with Specialist Teachers (American, Brazilian, Japanese, Swede)\r\nEditor : Magazine of revelation (3yrs)\r\nWinner of Songs writing Competition among 2400 participants in BS 2060 winner of dancing Competition in BS 2052\r\nCoordinator of National Motorbike Association, Nepal (1yr)\r\nTeaching in Hope Nepal Organization, Nepal (2yrs)\r\n\r\n<strong>Occupation</strong>\r\nVice President of Nepalese Development Society, Nepal\r\nTeacher : Resurrection Ecclesia for Youth\r\nPresident of Helping HEART Giving Hands Community ( Social Networ-None Profit Organization)\r\n\r\n<strong>Writer</strong>\r\nScript, Songs, Story, Short Film\r\nPublished Books : Novel (Baadhyatako Chakra); Book (What is sexuel desire?); (How to choose way of life?)\r\n\r\n<strong>Songs\r\n</strong> Dheri Dherai chot paayo; Timro yoban; Aakha Ramro; Dobato Ko; Ritto Sadakma; Charkiyo Mutu; Tipera joon; Binti mero (Nepali Film Milap)\r\n\r\n<strong>Short Film and Script :\r\n</strong>Gothalo), Aids Bhagaau Dirgayu Kamaau, Nakkali, Baajho Man, Mayaka Rangaharu, Aaina. Alchhe Sikari, Budho baagh, Paaniko Thopa, Maato Ko Thaal Ma Soon Ko Chamacha, Jibro ko khel, Haasne geeja, Andho Maya, Ke Jaat ka hau?, Baluwako Ghar, Kaanda ko jhyang and many more.\r\n\r\n<em> Writing is my Passion, Working together is my style, Confident and Daring is my Nature and to be Perfect is my aim. I Believe \"Action Speak louder than our speech \".</em>\r\n\r\nLast but not the Least, Thank You PMST Nepal for giving me excellent opportunity to recognize myself.', 'Om K Rai', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'om-k-rai', '', '', '2016-03-16 01:21:21', '2016-03-15 19:36:21', '', 0, 'http://pmstnepal.com/?post_type=team&#038;p=1690', 2, 'team', '', 0),
