(2012, 1, '2016-05-04 09:34:25', '2016-05-04 03:49:25', '<strong>Name</strong>: Bandhana K.C.\r\n<strong>DOB</strong>: 2048-01-19\r\n<strong>Address</strong>: Banasthali, Kathmandu, Nepal\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/pbandu.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2013\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-2013\" src=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/pbandu-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"pbandu\" width=\"660\" height=\"440\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong><u>Family Details</u></strong>\r\n<strong>Father</strong>: Kham Bahadur Khatri (Retired Inspector)\r\n<strong>Mother</strong>: Dhana Devi K.C.\r\n<strong>Sisters</strong>: Bhima, Kalika, Sanu, Srijana and Rekha\r\n\r\n<strong>Her Own Words</strong>:\r\nHi, I m Bhandhana K.C. with love my family and friends called me Bandu. I love Music and my passion on music started early from my childhood. I was born and grown up in Dolpa(a remote part of country).The only source of music and entertainment was a raido than. Now, i feel like radio was only my backbone on the time of learning. I used to listen the music on radio and practice it over and over with radio. I also known as talented and leading student on the back days of my school time.\r\n\r\nI had a very supportive parents. They keep inspiring me to pursue my career in the field of music. For my career I came to Kathmndu. I started music classes. With all my struggles and bad days i continue learning and singing i didnt give up. I want to be an Example and be an Icon. At once I had an opportunity to act in a short documentary as well..\r\n\r\nAfter 10 years of perseverance , I finally got an opportuity to sing and dance i my own song, Thank to PMST Nepal. I know this is just a start but i believe this is a entrance signal for my career and lot more to do ahead.\r\n\r\n<strong>Credit and supports</strong>:\r\nFirst to my family and for this grate opportunity I m very grateful to Lopsang Tamang, Om K Rai, Pema Man Singh Tamang and entire PMST Nepal Team for their Extra ordinary support. Without their help, it would not be possible.\r\n\r\n<strong>Fan of</strong>:\r\nI m biggest fan of Singer Sworup Raj Acharya..\r\n\r\n<strong>Inspiration and motivation</strong>:\r\nMy Family and Sworup Raj Achary is the most influential person for me.\r\n\r\n<strong>Discovering 1st Chance</strong>:\r\nI came to know about this project with the help of Lapsang Tamang and Om K Rai.\r\n\r\n<strong>Fan Follow link</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100010670169760&amp;ref=br_rs\">Facebook</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Song Title</strong>: Changa\r\n<strong>Compose</strong>: Himal Adhikari\r\n<strong>Lyrics</strong>: Om K Rai\r\n<strong>Music</strong>: Pema Man Singh Tamang\r\n\r\n<strong>Audio\r\n</strong>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/262404278&amp;color=ff5500&amp;auto_play=false&amp;hide_related=false&amp;show_comments=true&amp;show_user=true&amp;show_reposts=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"166\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\r\n\r\n<strong>Click : <a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/gallery/changa-video-shoot-photos/\">Video Shoot Photos</a> | <a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/video/changa-bandana-kc/\">Music Video</a></strong>', 'Bandana KC', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bandana-kc', '', '', '2016-05-12 15:07:45', '2016-05-12 09:22:45', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?post_type=1st_chance&#038;p=2012', 0, '1st_chance', '', 0),
