(2337, 1, '2017-06-21 11:29:17', '2017-06-21 05:44:17', '<h3>Migma Lama</h3>\r\n<strong>Name:</strong> Migma Lama\r\n<strong>DOB:</strong> 2054-08-17\r\n<strong>Address:</strong> Banaspati, Hetauda, Nepal\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/pf.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2338\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-2338\" src=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/pf-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"pf\" width=\"100%\" height=\"440\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Family Details</strong>\r\nFather: Chhiring Lama ( Ayurvedic Doctor )\r\nMother: Chitra Maya Lama\r\nBrother: Mikmar Lama, Sangey lama\r\n\r\nHi, I m Migma Lama . My family and friends calls me Kali with love. I m in love with music and have passion since my early childhood. I was born in beautiful place called Hetauda.\r\n\r\nI have such a supportive parents and they keep inspiring me towards my dream. i have started musical classes and continue to learn singing with different styles and techniques. although all my struggles and problems i didn\'t give up, i set myself as an example and icon in my dream which i want to show in real world. This is the reason i leave my birth place and came to Kathmandu.\r\n\r\nFinally, I got an opportunity to sing and act on my own song. I would like to thank PMST Nepal for this opportunity. I know, this is just a beginning or a green entrance signal towards my career and definitely, lot more stuff to do ahead.\r\n\r\n<strong>Credit and supports:</strong>\r\nFirst to my family and the opportunity by PMST Nepal 1st Chance project. I m very grateful to Suraj Yonjan, Pema Man Singh Tamang, Uman Waiba, Om K Rai, Dharma Bajra Lama and entire PMST Nepal Team for their Extra ordinary support.\r\n\r\n<strong>Fan of:</strong>\r\nI m biggest fan of singer Asha Bhosle..\r\n\r\n<strong>Inspiration and motivqtion:</strong>\r\nMy Family and Asha Bhosle is the most influential person for me.\r\n\r\n<strong>Song Title</strong>: Maya Chha Yeti Dherai\r\n<strong>Compose/Lyrics</strong>: Suraj Yonjan\r\n<strong>Music</strong>: Pema Man Singh Tamang\r\n\r\n<strong>Audio</strong>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/329210580&amp;color=ff5500&amp;auto_play=false&amp;hide_related=false&amp;show_comments=true&amp;show_user=true&amp;show_reposts=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"166\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>', 'Migma Lama', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'migma-lama', '', '', '2017-06-21 11:29:17', '2017-06-21 05:44:17', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?post_type=1st_chance&#038;p=2337', 0, '1st_chance', '', 0),
