(2493, 2, '2017-11-05 16:58:39', '2017-11-05 11:13:39', '<strong>Name:</strong> Dawa Chhiri Sherpa\n<strong>Nick Name :</strong> Dawadin\n<strong>DOB:</strong> 1991-4-2\n<strong>Address:</strong> Dolakha , Bigu , Nepal\n\n<a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/111.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-2492\" src=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/111-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a>\n<strong>\nFamily Details</strong>\n<strong>Father:</strong> Pemba sherpa\n<strong>Mother:</strong> Ngadolma sherpa\n<strong>Brother:</strong> Chang sherpa\n\n<strong>His Own Words :</strong>\nHi, I m Dawa sherpa . My family and friends calls me babu with love. I m in love with music and have passion since my early childhood. I was born in beautiful place called Dolakha.\n\nI have supportive parents . They keep  inspiring me towards my dream. I have started musical classes and continued to learn singing with different styles and techniques. Although all my struggles and problems I didn’t gave up, I set myself as an example and icon in my dream which I want to show in real world. This is the reason I left my birth place and came to Kathmandu.\nFinally, I got an opportunity to sing on my own song. I would like to thank <a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/\">PMST</a> Nepal for this opportunity. I know, this is just a beginning and  a green entrance signal towards my career and definitely,  lot more stuff to do ahead.\n\n<strong>Credit and supports:</strong>\nFirst to my family and the opportunity by PMST Nepal 1st Chance project. I m very grateful to suraj magar,shahas,chang sherpa and entire PMST Nepal Team for their Extra ordinary support.\n\n<strong>Fan of:</strong>\nI m biggest fan of singer Rajesh Pyal Rai.\n\n<strong>Inspiration and motivation:</strong>\nMy Family and Vikesh Nanda is the most influential person for me.\nSong Title: Nakali Kanchhi\nCompose/Lyrics: Take Ghising / Dawa Chhiri Sherpa\nMusic: Pema Man Singh Tamang\n<iframe src=\"https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/351368743&amp;color=%23ff5500&amp;auto_play=false&amp;hide_related=false&amp;show_comments=true&amp;show_user=true&amp;show_reposts=false&amp;show_teaser=true\" width=\"100%\" height=\"166\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>', 'Dawa Chhiri Sherpa', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2491-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-11-05 16:58:39', '2017-11-05 11:13:39', '', 2491, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/uncategorized/2491-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
