(2702, 1, '2018-04-19 11:14:53', '2018-04-19 05:29:53', '<div class=\"_4tdt _ua0\">\r\n<div class=\"_ua2\">\r\n<div class=\"_4tdv\">\r\n<div class=\"_5wd4 _1nc6\">\r\n<div class=\"_h8t\">\r\n<div id=\"js_3hg\" class=\"_5wd9 direction_ltr\" data-tooltip-content=\"Wednesday 6:36am\" data-hover=\"tooltip\" data-tooltip-position=\"right\">\r\n<div class=\"_5wde _n4o\">\r\n<div class=\"_5w1r _3_om _5wdf\">\r\n<div class=\"_4gx_\">\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mongolian-heart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2696\" src=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mongolian-heart.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"_d97\"><span class=\"_5yl5\">Mongolian Heart is celebrating silver jubilee with there 25 songs, which is a successful Nepali Band and performing live music with an audience of listeners and viewers with the lyrics of \'Ubho Ubho Khasa Ma Jada\', \'Na Tanu Ta Tanu Lagne\'. </span></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"_d97\"><span class=\"_5yl5\">Mongolian Heart, which became very popular in Nepalese Nepali musical industry, has been concerting and celebrating silver jubilee on 8th Baisakh this coming Saturday in Hyatt Regency Ground in Tussal.</span></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"_d97\"><span class=\"_5yl5\"> Singer Raju Lama told the members of \'Mangolian Heart\' will join the famous and well-known singers / singers in the Concert. He told that silver jubilee should keep the love and courage sustained by the audience and the source with his promise of his journey. </span></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"_d97\"><span class=\"_5yl5\">This musical band has many popular songs Among them are \'Ubho Ubho Khasa Ma Jada\', \'Na Tanu Ta Tanu Lagne\', \'Timilai dhe khera \', \'Mero Nepal\' and more. \'Mangolian Heart\' is considered to be a success in the crowd of musical bands. This band once again has taken the view of the viewer and audience of \'Heart\' According to Raju, \'Mangolian Heart\' has planned to concert more than dozens of different places in the country within 2075 years. </span></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"_d97\"><span class=\"_5yl5\"> Concert to be held at the Hyatt Regency Ground is also a charity. Chartity tickets have been like a coincidence while the ticket has been set up at the cost of Rs.25 .</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Mongolian Heart is going to celebrating their silver jubilee on 8th Baisakh this coming Saturday in Hyatt Regency Ground - Tussal.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2695-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-04-19 11:14:53', '2018-04-19 05:29:53', '', 2695, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/uncategorized/2695-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3209, 1, '2018-08-14 21:17:42', '2018-08-14 15:32:42', 'Singer Pragya Lama has came up with the freshest new songs \"Sano Hamro Ghar\". New Nepali Song of the new singer Pragya Lama has released her video of the \"little Sano Hamro Ghar\". Prakash Lama has Composed the song, while Udayra Poudel has arranged the song. Riya Lama and Sandesh Pandey was featureing in the music video with very beautiful act.\n\nThe song was choreographed by Priya Lama and music video was Directed by Dharma Bajra Lama, Cinematographed by Yodin Yonjan. Drone Pilot and Edit done by Pema Man Sing Tamang.\n\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1U_cDnVcqIg\" width=\"706\" height=\"397\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>', 'New comer Pragya Dumjan Lama\'s \"Sano Hamro Ghar\" has Released Worldwide (Watch the Music Video)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3206-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-08-14 21:17:42', '2018-08-14 15:32:42', '', 3206, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/uncategorized/3206-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2706, 1, '2018-04-23 07:50:35', '2018-04-23 02:05:35', 'Mongolian Heart has come a long way since their inception in 1992 and are ‘Thankful, Grateful, Blessed’ to  celebrate 25 years in music marking it with a live concert at the Hyatt Ground, Chuchepati Kathmandu on April 21.\r\n\r\nThey also launched their album ‘Mongolian Heart: Volume 7’ on this special occasion. The concert is also a charity event with earnings from tickets donated to Tusal Youth Club. The band now intends to perform 25 concerts all around Nepal in the 2075 calendar year before Dashain.\r\n\r\n[gallery ids=\"2707,2708,2709,2710,2712,2713\"]', 'Mongolian Heart Celebrates Their 25th Anniversary', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'mongolian-heart-celebrates-their-25th-anniversary', '', '', '2018-04-23 07:52:28', '2018-04-23 02:07:28', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=2706', 0, 'post', '', 0),
