(2717, 1, '2018-04-23 18:30:29', '2018-04-23 12:45:29', '<a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Tirupati_English_Boarding_High_School.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-2719\" src=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Tirupati_English_Boarding_High_School-1024x678.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"660\" height=\"437\" /></a>\r\n\r\nTirupati English Boarding High School is located in a quiet and silent site at Budanilkhantha, Kathmandu, Nepal. As an established co-educational academy running up to Secondary School level, the school has taken multifarious objectives with its sacred motto ‘Wisdom Wins World’ for growing students in their all-round development. Since its first inception, the school has glorious history of decent academic achievement both in quality and quantity.\r\n\r\nThere are more than 100 institutional schools operating in budhanilkantha municipality area. Excluding some of the schools, most of the schools are in the same way and they are all identical when Teaching. However, the Tirupati English Boarding high school, located in ward 10 Baluwakhani, is different than other schools. This school, which has been teaching in a special preference to technology and ritual, has been in a very strong way for the past three years. There are more than three hundred students in this school started with 10 students. Students participate in SEE exams had succeeded in bringing out the excellent results.', 'Tirupati English Boarding High School Establishing as an Excellent School', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tirupati-english-boarding-high-school', '', '', '2018-04-23 18:38:42', '2018-04-23 12:53:42', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=2717', 0, 'post', '', 0),
