(2814, 1, '2017-01-15 09:03:12', '2017-01-15 03:18:12', '<div class=\"_xlr\">\n<div id=\"id_587ae4855df893b76334033\" class=\"text_exposed_root text_exposed\">Confirmed :\nLONDON, Jan 14: Famous rapper Anil Adhikari, known with a stage name Yama Buddha, has been found dead here on Saturday morning.\n<a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/YAMABUDDHAZ.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2201\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-2201\" src=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/YAMABUDDHAZ-620x1024.jpg\" alt=\"YAMABUDDHAZ\" width=\"620\" height=\"1024\" /></a>\nAdhikari’s brother-in-law Resh Marhatta confirmed the death talking to Republica Online.BBC Nepali Service quoting the family sources said that the rapper is no more.\nAccording to family sources, the singer was found dead in his bathroom at around 3 am. Adhi<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">kari, 30, had been living in London with his wife.\n.\nThe dead body has been kept at Northwick Park Hospital, Harrow.\n\nSource added that police have told the family members to contact them only on Monday. It is learnt that the postmortem will be conducted on Wednesday.\nMarhatta added that the cause for the death will be known only after the postmortem.</span></div>\n<span id=\"fbPhotoSnowliftTagList\" class=\"fbPhotoTagList\"><span class=\"fcg\"> — with <span class=\"fbPhotoTagListTag tagItem\"><a class=\"taggee\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100008618658498\" data-tag=\"100008618658498\" data-hovercard=\"/ajax/hovercard/hovercard.php?id=100008618658498&amp;type=mediatag&amp;media_info=6.1119313144857885\" data-hovercard-prefer-more-content-show=\"1\">विशाल सागर</a></span>.</span></span>\n<div id=\"fbPhotoSnowliftProductsTagList\" class=\"pts fbPhotoProductsTagList\"></div>\n<div id=\"fbPhotoSnowliftLegacyTagList\" class=\"pts fbPhotoLegacyTagList\"></div>\n<div id=\"fbPhotoSnowliftCallToActionButton\" class=\"fbPhotosPhotoButtons\"></div>\n<div id=\"fbPhotoSnowliftOwnerButtons\" class=\"mvm fbPhotosPhotoOwnerButtons stat_elem\"></div>\n<div id=\"fbPhotoSnowliftOriginalStory\" class=\"_56lj\"></div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"fbPhotoSnowliftFundraiser\"></div>\n<div id=\"fbPhotoSnowliftViews\" class=\"_4p3v\"></div>\n<div id=\"fbPhotoSnowliftFeedback\" class=\"fbPhotosSnowliftFeedback\"></div>', 'Confirmed : Famous rapper Yama Buddha, has been found dead on Saturday morning at London.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'famous-rapper-anil-adhikari-known-stage-name-yama-buddha-found-dead-saturday-morning', '', '', '2017-01-15 09:03:12', '2017-01-15 03:18:12', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?post_type=gallery&amp;p=2199', 58, 'post', '', 0),
