(2976, 1, '2018-06-14 12:36:13', '2018-06-14 06:51:13', 'Jun 13, 2018-Miss Nepal 2010 Sadiccha Shrestha has been appointed as the official choreographer of Miss Nepal North America slated to be held on August 11, 2018.\r\n\r\nMiss Nepal North America is an international pageant and a global platform for the \"Nepali women of tomorrow\". This is the first pageant where all Nepali young women between the age of 18-27 living in Canada, Mexico, United States and other North American countries can participate.\r\n\r\nSadiccha Shrestha represented Nepal in Miss World in 2010. She is the recipient of Nepal Bidhya Bhusan Padak 2017, MBA Gold Medalist, and the Nepal Tourism Ambassador of the year 2011.\r\n\r\nDuring her tenure as Miss Nepal 2010, she was also appointed as Young Conservation Ambassador for WWF. She also won the titles of Miss Personality, Miss Best Walk and Miss Photogenic. She became the contestant to win the highest number of subtitles in Miss Nepal. She was also awarded as the VOW Top 10 College Women Competition.\r\n\r\nLikewise, Fatena Qassem, Miss Tourism Intercontinental 2018, has been appointed as the official trainer for the event. Apart from that, she holds titles of Miss Woman New York 2017, and Miss Tourism USA 2017.\r\n\r\nProfessor at the NYIT School of Hospitality - School of Management Hospitality Studies , Fatena Qassem is also a hospitality veteran of 20 years serving the industry. She also assists NYC mayor’s office and state’s commitment for better Sustainable future.\r\n\r\nThe Grand Finale and the VIP after party of the event will be held at Melrose Ballroom, Queens, New York. Melrose Ballroom is one of the best venues in New York where internationally acclaimed artists like Rihanna, Shawn Mendes, Steven Tyler, and FKA Twigs, Bipul Chettri, The Edge Band, The Original Duo, Mukti And Revival, The Nepali Idols, Naren Limbu, Cobweb and many more have graced the staged.', 'Sadichha official choreographer of Miss Nepal N America', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sadichha-official-choreographer-of-miss-nepal-n-america', '', '', '2018-06-14 12:36:29', '2018-06-14 06:51:29', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=2976', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(2923, 1, '2018-06-08 23:28:33', '2018-06-08 17:43:33', '<b>Devika Bandana</b> is a Nepalese solo and playback singer. She has received many national level awards and has been singing in the music field for a long time. She has recenlty released her second hindi romantic number  \"Ab Dil Zara Zara\".\r\n\r\nFeaturing Bollywood artist Parul Gulati and Nepali artist Anoop Bikram Shahi  in the video. Vijesh Poudel has directed the video. The video of this song is now on  YouTube channel.\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/gWiFMwmyWNA\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>', 'VENUS Presents latest Hindi Video Song of 2018 \"Ab Dil Zara Zara\"  In the voice of \"Devika Bandana\".', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'venus-presents-latest-hindi-video-song-of-2018-ab-dil-zara-zara-in-the-voice-of-devika-bandana', '', '', '2018-06-08 23:30:48', '2018-06-08 17:45:48', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=2923', 0, 'post', '', 0),
