(2931, 1, '2018-06-12 09:39:21', '2018-06-12 03:54:21', '<h2><strong>Top 10 Dance Crew From Nepal 2018</strong></h2>\r\nFrom the past few years, we see lots of dance crew formed in Nepal. The craze of dance in the recent days has been raised with the growth of social media especially Youtube and Facebook. Different dance crew members have brought a mixture of the cultural Nepali and western Hip-Hop dance in the field. We have listed top 10 best dance crew from Nepal and ranking on the basis of their popularity and views.\r\n<h2>#1. VIBE &amp; WAVE – Dance Studio Nepal</h2>\r\nVIBE &amp; WAVE – Dance Studio Nepal is creative and talented group of Nepali youngsters. The studio is located in New Baneshwor and the team has been uploading amazing videos on a weekly basis. The latest dance (cover) <strong><em>Man Magan</em></strong> have gathered whooping 2.4 M+ views within a week and it grabbed the #1 Trending spot for few days.  <strong>VIBE &amp; WAVE Dance Studio </strong>no. 1 dance team from Nepal as of now(2018).\r\n<h3>Latest Dance Performance</h3>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/bjdv0vWmDzA\" width=\"760\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe>\r\n<h2>#2. Cartoonz Crew</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nCartoonz Crew is the one and only best dance crew based in Kathmandu Nepal. Each and every dance they perform grab the Trending #1 on Youtube Nepal. This team was formed back in 2010 with team members including Saroj Adhikari, Ashma BK, Bikash Rai, Lakpa D Lama, Ram Gurung, Subin Adhikari. Cartoonz Crew is a B-Boying/Hip-Hop Dance Crew who have won following titles in the dance field.\r\n\r\nBOTY Nepal 2012/13- Battle, Best Show Winner!!\r\nBOTY Nepal 2013- Battle, Runner Up.\r\nR16 Nepal 2014-Battle, Runner Up.\r\nWorld Leisure Games 2015, Streetdance- Silver medal.\r\n<h3>Latest Dance Performance</h3>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KYYvY3cyeKI\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe>\r\n<h2>#3. The Wild Ripperz Crew</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>The wild Ripperz Crew</strong> is 1st runner-up of Dance Plus Season 2. The first crew to represent Nepal in Indian dancing reality show.This crew has a total of 13 crew members. This crew has placed in the 1st runner-up in Dance Plus season 2, Winner of India’s Best Dance Crew 2016 and <span class=\"text_exposed_show\">Winner of India’s Biggest (V) fest 2015</span>.\r\n\r\nThe team member includes Ron Singh, Kiran Singh, Surain Rai, Buddha Lama, Sagar Rai, Santosh Darji, Saul James, Suraj Ido, Suman syangtan, Pawan Singh, Ganesh Mali, Harikesh Kori, KETAN KAPOOR. Because of the platform, they are performing this crew ma top place on the list of <strong>Top 10 Dance Crew From Nepal.</strong>\r\n<h3><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">Latest Dance Performance</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/b-zIweUG0Ew\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></span></h3>\r\n<h2>#4. Sabin Karki “Beest” and Crew</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThis team has a huge fan following in Nepal after their dance performance in <strong>Viral Vaidiyo</strong>. Sabin Karki “Beest” a former crew member of <a href=\"http://www.nepalitrends.com/real-story-of-cartoonz-crew-and-sabin-karki-beest-controversy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><em>The Cartoonz Crew</em></strong></a> has formed this group. This group is now busy performing in the various show across Nepal. This group member includes Sabik Karki “Beest”, Diksha Thakuri (8 Years old), Merry Khatri, Sabrina Gurung Flow, <span id=\"fb-timeline-cover-name\" class=\"_2t_q\" data-testid=\"profile_name_in_profile_page\">Xiring Theeng and Shankar Kakku Dhungana.</span>\r\n<h3>Latest Dance Performance</h3>\r\n<h2><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NDKkuOuRwJw\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe>\r\n#5. The NEXT Team (NEpalese-EXtreme)</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe NeXt is abbreviated after the Nepalese extreme, which truly aims to provide the quality of entertainment. This team is Sydney based Nepali dance group specialized in true entertainment. Officially formed in 2014, with the motto of keeping the “awe!” factor up and leave a posit<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">ive impact on the viewers. Working on meeting the expectations each and every time. This team came into limelight after the cover dance of <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CPm-Zl-NZr8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><em>Jaalma</em></strong></a>. Some of the best dance by this crew are <strong><em><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9EwJFu8RIIU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mitho</a></em></strong>, </span>FUNTASTIC (PANI PARYO) and Nepathya Song.\r\n\r\nCrew members include Pradeep Lama, Amit Bajracharya, Prabha Dawadi, Surakcha Thapa, Amar Tamang (Dovz),Shazia Miya,  Tsering Angmo, Suchana Paudel.\r\n<h3>Latest Dance Performance</h3>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/CSLxLKspxGE\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe>\r\n<h2>#6. Bhimphedi Guys</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBhimphedi Guys are Nepal based dance crew who has performed in dozens of Nepali music videos. This team is very energetic dance team with their own identity in the dance field. The crew member includes leader Nirmal Lama, Mithun Lama, Bisaan Lama, Anjan Lama, Manjit Lama, Sabin Lama.\r\n\r\nThis crew made number 5th position in the list of <strong><em>Top 10 Best Dance Crew From Nepal.</em></strong>\r\n<h3>Latest Dance Performance</h3>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YIoQkN_U6FE\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe>\r\n<h2>#7. Kristal Klaws</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nKristal Klaws dance crew is Pokhara based dance crew. Recently this team has won the Cover dance competition of Mr. Jholey film organized by the Cinema Arts Nepal. The team member includes leader Sandesh Jung Rana, Dev Gurung, Prakriti Magar, Kushal Nepali, Sudhir Nepali and Prabin Magar. Some of the best dance by this crew are Bau Bajeko Palama, Nira cover Dance, Jali Rumal etc. These group is one of the rising stars of Nepal.\r\n<h3>Recent Dance Performance</h3>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Cvc5N958usY\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe>\r\n<h2>#8. STRUK POP DANCE CREW</h2>\r\nSTRUKPOP is also a winner of KPOP WORLD FESTIVAL 2016. This crew member includes Suresh Moktan, Suman Rai, Alek Tamang, Mizel Raj Pradhan, Prakash Rai, Priya Limbu, Ashish Tamang, Santosh Shah Thakuri.\r\n<h3>Latest Dance Performance</h3>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ktqxdOXI7x0\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe>\r\n<h2><span id=\"channel-title\" class=\"style-scope ytd-c4-tabbed-header-renderer\">#9. The New Ktm Dance Studio</span></h2>\r\nThis is newly formed dance group based in Kathmandu Nepal. Formally the group was associated with the Aashis Malla youtube channel. Now this group is associated with The New Ktm Dance Studio. This team has made number 9 position in the list of <strong><em>Top 10 Best Dance Crew From Nepal</em></strong>.\r\n<h3>Latest Dance Performance</h3>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/15WYL2I0auI\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe>\r\n<h2><span id=\"channel-title\" class=\"style-scope ytd-c4-tabbed-header-renderer\">#10. </span>De Dynamic Crew</h2>\r\nThis crew made number 10 position in the list of <strong><em>Top 10 Best Dance Crew From Nepal</em></strong>.  The energetic team member includes Dipak Narayan Singh Bibek Thing (A.k.A Bboy Like) Ravi Thapa Magar (A.K.A Bboy Clown) Ravi Bholan (A.k.A Bboy Duke) Sudip Chaudhary.\r\n<h3>Latest Dance Performance</h3>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LK8eyoLXbfk\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nEven though Cartoonz Crew is considered as one of the best crew in Nepal, <strong>VIBE &amp; WAVE Dance Studio</strong><strong>Nepa</strong>l has been listed at the top of the list. <strong>Maybe Cartoonz Crew</strong> tops the list soon but let’s see how Ripperz and other crew go ahead with progress. This post is updated frequently to keep the information fresh.', 'Top 10 Dance Crew From Nepal 2018', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'top-10-dance-crew-from-nepal-2018', '', '\nhttp://www.nepalitrends.com/real-story-of-cartoonz-crew-and-sabin-karki-beest-controversy/', '2018-06-12 09:39:21', '2018-06-12 03:54:21', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=2931', 0, 'post', '', 0),
