(3036, 1, '2018-06-30 16:07:10', '2018-06-30 10:22:10', 'Famous Actress and Model Sushma Adhikari was handed with Best Female Model in recently held music award in Malaysia’s Grand Hotel.\r\n\r\nShe started her modelling journey through the song ‘Rog ho ki dosh ho’ and has acted in over 200+ music videos till date. She is now consider as one of the finest face of Nepali Cine world.\r\n\r\nSushma Adhikari made her cinematic debut with \"Anoutho Prem Katha\" A film by Kanchan Shahi. The film did average business at box office. Thereafter, a series of successful films followed such as \"Pipal \"and \"Deewaana2\". Sushma next successful movie was \"Jay Madesh\". Her performance in \"Jay Madesh\" is well praise by Tarai (plan) audience and she became a sensation in Tarai region of Nepal till date. She also played in the super hit music video \" Ghumera Julfai - Popular Teej (folk) Song \" and \"Mero Dhadkan\" sung by well known singer Rajesh Payal Rai and other hundreds of contemporary, and Folk Music Videos.\r\n\r\nSome of her super hit movies includes \"Anautho Prem Katha, Peepal, Diwana 2, Khurpa and currently working in three different movies which are due to release in 2017.\r\n\r\n[gallery size=\"large\" columns=\"1\" ids=\"3040,3041,3037,3039,3042\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Famous Actress and Model Sushma Adhikari was awarded the Best Female Model held in Malaysia’s Grand Hotel.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'famous-actress-and-model-sushma-adhikari-was-awarded-the-best-female-model-held-in-malaysias-grand-hotel', '', '', '2018-06-30 16:16:31', '2018-06-30 10:31:31', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=3036', 0, 'post', '', 0),
