(3179, 1, '2018-08-08 11:51:15', '2018-08-08 06:06:15', 'Kathmandu, Singer Ryan Karki, \"Jaha Ma\" was released. Singer as well as well known musician Ryan Karki\'s New song \"Jaha Ma\" music video has been published in youtube as well.\r\n\r\nThis video has been shot in the scenic spot of Sindhuli and Om Prasai has done the best cinematography where Suresh rai has hosted Production Manager. The singer himself is also a well-known music video director, we can see Kausal Nepal and Anju Chaulagai act in the music video.\r\n\r\nDirector Karki says this video is very beautifully presented and Audio of this music video has already been popular in radio broadcasted in Kantipur. Live Music Highlights Pvt. Ltd has been taken the responsibility for market management and production of this song.\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dbzBqwk22YQ\" width=\"706\" height=\"397\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>', 'Ryan Karki\'s \"Jaha Ma\" has released.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ryan-karkis-jaha-ma-has-released', '', '', '2018-08-08 12:12:56', '2018-08-08 06:27:56', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=3179', 0, 'post', '', 0),
