(3215, 1, '2018-08-19 12:19:35', '2018-08-19 06:34:35', '<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Actor Puspa Khadka has been confirmed for the upcoming movie Dal Bhat Tarkari.  To add a beauty to the film, Swastima Khadka will be playing as Puspa\'s co-actor.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">However official signing has yet to be done by the actors.  Actor puspa said \" I have negotiated with Kiran Dai and we have got  positive response from Swastima too.  But I and Swastima both hadn\'t officially signed the film.  However, it is confirmed.\"</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Film director Kiran KC ensured that everything is set, Puspa and Swastima will be playing the lead role in the film and other actors of the film will be confirmed soon.  Film \"Dal Bhat Tarkari\" is being directed by Sudan KC; son of Kiran KC.  Multistarrer movie will have the pivotal role of Niruta Singh, Priyanka Karki, Pushpa Khadka, Swastima Khadka, barsha Raut, Anurag Man Singh Kunwar, Rajaram Poudel, Shiva Hari Poudel including Madan Krishna and Hari Bansha.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/maha-jodi-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3219\" src=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/maha-jodi-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"702\" height=\"635\" /></a></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">The film will set on theater on Baisakh 23, 2076.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"yj6qo ajU\">\r\n<div id=\":ki\" class=\"ajR\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Hide expanded content\" data-tooltip=\"Hide expanded content\"><img class=\"ajT\" src=\"https://ssl.gstatic.com/ui/v1/icons/mail/images/cleardot.gif\" /></div>\r\n</div>', 'Actor Puspa has been confirmed for the upcoming movie \"Dal Bhat Tarkari\"', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'actor-puspa-has-been-confirmed-for-the-upcoming-movie-dal-bhat-tarkari', '', '', '2018-08-19 12:32:33', '2018-08-19 06:47:33', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=3215', 0, 'post', '', 0),
