(3226, 1, '2018-08-22 12:01:48', '2018-08-22 06:16:48', 'Love finds its way and so we have another odd celebrity couple making headlines these days. What is the age when it comes to love? Age, race, nationality, status are nothing but social standards that are labeled on us. But they mean virtually nothing when the love is pure; the heart finds its way.\r\n\r\nThe past Saturday, Nick Jonas, and Priyanka Chopra, held a Roka ceremony confirming their engagement. “The only way to do this with Family and God. Thank you all for your wishes and blessings,” These were Priyanka Chopra’s official caption words on the massive wave of engagement photos on Instagram. The cutest thing is how Nick has posted the same number of pictures in almost the same order as Priyanka. The two have surpassed social boundaries of all kinds and accepted each other for who they are.\r\n\r\nFans all around the world dearly adore them, but some cringe at the idea as well. Is it the difference in their race? No, fortunately, the world has moved past racism. Well, it’s fairly obvious. It’s the 11 year age difference and not the conventional older guy younger womenkind. Nick is reportedly 11 years younger than his fiancé at just 25 years of age at the moment. His history of dating makes it evident that he’s more attracted to older women. But his peers always confirm that Nick is far mature for his age. Nick has already dated many celebrities like, Taylor Swift, Miley Cyrus, Kate Hudson who were older than him at the time.\r\n\r\nNick obviously finds Priyanka very attractive and not just because of her age. He thinks of her as a beautiful, intelligent person with a charisma that he couldn’t resist being drawn to. Priyanka agrees to Nick being very mature and so the couple is now close to tying the knots. After two months of dating, the couple has now begun the series of pre-wedding ceremonies as per the Indian rituals. The world is eagerly waiting for the big wedding now which sources tell to be pretty soon in the future.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPriyanka Chopra And Nick Jonas confirm they are into Next Level', 'Priyanka Chopra And Nick Jonas confirm they are into Next Level', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'priyanka-chopra-and-nick-jonas-confirm-they-are-into-next-level', '', '', '2018-08-22 12:01:48', '2018-08-22 06:16:48', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=3226', 0, 'post', '', 0),
