(3240, 1, '2018-08-29 06:13:21', '2018-08-29 00:28:21', 'Shahas started to rap since from his childdood and music is his passion.\r\n\r\nHe believe in struggle and hard work. He just like to create lyrics when he feel good,happy,sad,upset n when he see real things around him. He’ve been underground rapper for few years and Pmstnepal 1st change project let him to record and released his 1st official video \"Sakdina hola\" on the producton of Pmstnepal Studio.\r\n\r\nShahas is one of the upcoming biggest young rap stars. He drops a song, it instantly becomes a hit online all of his songs have garnered a excellent views on YouTube.\r\n\r\nIn 2017, he released the music video Sakdina hola a song that talked about Nerver give up just keep working hard. After a little over a year, Shahas has put out a new song called \"Mero Soch\".Song talked about feeling lost and finding the way again . Both the videos are directed by Pema Man Singh Tamang.\r\n\r\nWritten and performed by Shahas himeself, \"Mero Soch\" also features Pema Man Singh Tamang on vocals.\r\n\r\nWatch the music video that has already released in youtube.\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8xxcdZgTyFs\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\r\n\r\nMore video of Shahas:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VlrSDAUWnWs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VlrSDAUWnWs</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XlsbDsL9Q9g\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XlsbDsL9Q9g</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U71ZwJpc0g8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U71ZwJpc0g8</a>', 'Shahas New Music Video \"Malai Khoja\" after his 2017 hit \"Sakdina hola\"', 'https://youtu.be/8xxcdZgTyFs', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'shahas-new-music-video-malai-khoja-after-his-2017-hit-sakdina-hola', '