(3252, 1, '2018-09-03 17:34:46', '2018-09-03 11:49:46', '<strong>The first trailer of ‘Katha Kathmandu’ starring Priyanka Karki, Pramod Agrahari, Ayushman Desraj Joshi, Sandhya KC among others is all about.</strong>\r\n\r\nMakers of the movie have released the trailer on Sunday amid press meet. The movie is directed by Sangita Shrestha, who had directed a serial in Kantipur TV before, now came up with very first feature. The movie has been produced by Bijaya Rai under the banner of Aahana Films.\r\n\r\nThe trailers treat us with bold and dark part of capital city, where especially women’s are living with pain and sorrow. Priyanka is in pivotal role and Pramod has been also played parallel characters.\r\n\r\nThe movie is slated to release on 12th Asoj, 2075.\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/s_57rsKUPjU\" width=\"702\" height=\"395\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>', 'Watch :  Trailer of ‘Katha Kathmandu’', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3250-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-03 17:34:46', '2018-09-03 11:49:46', '', 3250, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/uncategorized/3250-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
