(3417, 1, '2018-11-12 21:02:07', '2018-11-12 15:17:07', 'The film \'Summer Love\' is based on the famous novel \'Summer Love\' by Subin Bhattari is releasing on Feb 08. The production team has published the main posters of the film featuring Suraj Singh Thakuri, Namrata Sapkota, Ashish Piya and Revati Chhetri.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Final1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-3419\" src=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Final1-711x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"660\" height=\"951\" /></a>\r\n\r\nAshish and Revati are debuting from the movie. While coming back to the movie, Ashish has a background in modeling while Revati is a Miss International winner from India. She has had some experience in acting in India. Revati has already been working in the film like \'Gangs of Northwest\', \'Khatun\', \'Happy Pher Bhag Jayagi\'.\r\n\r\nThe film had directed by Muskan Dhakal. He had earlier directed \'Nai Na Vanula Part 3\'. The film had to work hard to complete the hip of the book. Now we are ready to make the movie as expected to the audience, Dhakal said.\r\n\r\nSubin\'s story has been featured in Samipya Raj Timilsina\'s script, and the film\'s dialogue had written by Subin and Samipya Raj. Khagendra Shrestha and Indra Bhandari are the producers, while Binod Adhikari is executive producers in the film made in Nightingale Entertainment\'s banner.', 'Sharing the Love this Valentine\'s Day \'Summer Love\'', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sharing-the-love-this-valentines-day-summer-love', '', '', '2018-11-12 21:24:23', '2018-11-12 15:39:23', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=3417', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(3265, 1, '2018-09-04 11:58:44', '2018-09-04 06:13:44', 'Not as much as seven days after Eminem aim at Machine Gun Kelly on his unexpected collection Kamikaze, the latter has fired back at his previous icon with the diss track \"Rap Devil.\"\r\n\r\nA play off Eminem\'s 2013 track \"Rap God,\" MGK\'s \"Rap Devil\" dumps on everything from Em\'s \"bizarre\" facial hair to being \"calm and exhausted.\" It just deteriorates from that point, as Kelly calls attention to that Eminem\'s \"last four collections\" were \"as awful as your selfie,\" and blames Marshall Mathers for utilizing his director Paul Rosenberg to attempt and retire MGK\'s career\r\n\r\nOn his new Kamikaze track \"Not Alike,\" Eminem addresses MGK\'s comments about his daughter, rapping, \"And I’m talking to you but you already know who the fuck you are, Kelly/ I don’t use sublims and sure as f--- don’t sneak-diss/ But keep commenting on my daughter Hailie.\"\r\n\r\nOn Monday (Sept. 3), MGK defended \"Rap Devil\" on Twitter, writing that he\'s standing up for his \"generation\" amid Eminem\'s attack.\r\n\r\n\"Im standing up for not just myself, but my generation,\" Kelly wrote. \"im doing the same shit you did back in ur day. life is still real on my side, and i had to take time from the grind to defend myself from someone i called an idol. love, Rap Devil.\"\r\n\r\nListen to MGK\'s \"Rap Devil\" below.\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4sNCyiyIc_8\" width=\"620\" height=\"376\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>', 'MGK\'s fired back at his former idol Eminem with the diss track \"Rap Devil.\": Listen', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'mgks-fired-back-at-his-former-idol-eminem-with-the-diss-track-rap-devil-listen', '', '', '2018-09-04 11:58:44', '2018-09-04 06:13:44', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=3265', 0, 'post', '', 0),
