(3275, 1, '2018-09-05 18:29:01', '2018-09-05 12:44:01', 'Tamang Movie \"Serku\" has released its trailer through the lhapsang Karpo YouTube channel. The two songs of this movie directed by Rajkumar Moktan has been successfu <span class=\"css-133coio etbu2a32\">cherished </span>by the audience. The current prominent tamang vovie actress Sushma Moktan and Sushma Thing have been shown as disabled.\r\n\r\nAbout eight years later, the trailer has presented Chadani Mokan and Shyam Yonzan as a couple in the movie. In the trailer, Bikash Syangtan has been presented as an enemy of love. The specific thing is not yet confirmation? To know the whole story should wait till the release date.\r\n\r\n\"Serku\" is different from other Tamang movies, directed on the basis of the Tamang Myth around the Bel Mountain of Okhaldhunga district. Eminen artists from Tamang movie industry, who were casting in different characters in \'Serku Movie\', were named Chadani Moktan, Rituraj Pakhrin, Sushma Thing, Sushma Moktan, Urmila Waiba, the well-known villain Bikash Syangtan, Shyam Lal Yonzan, Bairagi Moktan, MuskanTamang, Yogesh Moktan, Kiran Tamang, Gopiram Tamang, Nima Rumba and many other actors have been acting.\r\n\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/x-hSrkjKZJo\" width=\"100%\" height=\"369\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><span data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span></iframe>', 'Most Awaited Tamang Movie \'Serku\' an Indigenous Featured Film by Raj Kumar Moktan ft. Rituraj Pakhrin, Urmila Waiba set to release within the next “few days” Bhadra 30th in Rastriya naach ghar. (Watch the Trailer)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'most-awaited-tamang-movie-serku-an-indigenous-featured-film-by-raj-kumar-moktan-ft-rituraj-pakhrin-urmila-waiba-set-to-release-within-the-next-few-days-bhadra-30th-in-rastriya', '', '', '2018-09-05 21:38:49', '2018-09-05 15:53:4