(3277, 1, '2018-09-05 18:29:01', '2018-09-05 12:44:01', 'Tamang Movie Serku has released its trailer through the lhapsang Karpo YouTube channel. The two songs of this movie directed by Rajkumar Moktan already been successful liked by the audience. The current prominent Susma Moktan and Susma Thing have been shown as disabled.\r\n\r\nAbout eight years later, the trailer has presented Chardi Mokan and Shyam Yonjan as couples in this movie. In the trailer, Bikash Syangtan has been presented as an enemy of love. The specific thing is no confirmation yet? To know the whole story one should wait till the release date.\r\n\r\n\"Serku\" is different from other Tamang movies, directed by the basis of the Tamang Myth around the Bell Mountain of Okhaldhunga district. Famous artists from Tamang movie industry, who were casting in different characters in \'Serku Movie\', were named Chadani Moktan, Rituraj Pakhrin, Sushma Thing, Sushma Moktan, Urmila Waiba, the well-known villain Bikash Syangtan, Shyam Lal Yozan, Bairagi Moktan, MuskanTamang, Yogesh Moktan, Kiran Tamang, Gopiram Tamang, Nima Rumba and many other actors have been acting.\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/x-hSrkjKZJo\" width=\"100%\" height=\"369\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><span data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span></iframe>', 'Most Awaited Tamang Movie \'Serku\' an Indigenous Featured Film by Raj Kumar Moktan ft. Rituraj Prakhrin , Urmila Waiba only few days to release in Big Cinema halls. (Watch the Trailer)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3275-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-05 18:29:01', '2018-09-05 12:44:01', '', 3275, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/uncategorized/3275-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
