(3365, 1, '2018-10-09 21:45:34', '2018-10-09 16:00:34', 'Noren &amp; Nhyuwave Band was Formed in 2017, That is when Noren was doing solo song later he introduce Max awale and Mahesh Shakya and formed Noren &amp; Nhyuwave Band , Later in 2018 Noren again introduced pabitra gurung a female vocalist for band Together they are part of the city’s growing indie.in 2017 they released debut RnB song Khojchu timi lai Through song Nepal YouTube channel which is one of popular YouTube channel in Nepal. From then they had done lots of songs already released through different YouTube channels and National TV channels.\r\nNoren &amp; Nhyuwave are known for their hard work, humble attitude, and passionate dedication and commitment to their music.\r\nCurrently they are busy with their new official song name kanchi which is going to release soon through PMST Nepal.', 'Noren & Nhyuwave Band new official song \"kanchi\" which is going to release soon through PMST Nepal.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'noren-nhyuwave-band-new-official-song-kanchi-which-is-going-to-release-soon-through-pmst-nepal', '', '', '2018-10-09 21:45:34', '2018-10-09 16:00:34', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=3365', 0, 'post', '', 0),
