(3378, 1, '2018-10-13 06:54:57', '2018-10-13 01:09:57', 'Dashain is the grandest, longest and most auspicious festival in Nepal. Dashain is celebrated by the whole country for the goddess Durga\'s victory over the demon Mahishasura. In addition to worship the Goddess Durga, Nepalis will hold celebrations for the fertility of the land and a year of good harvest. Meanwhile, Dasain has also emphasized the importance of the family reunion, which is helpful to ease social contradictions.\r\n\r\nOn this festive occasion ON THE ROCKS bring their song \"Dashain ko Jutta\" which was released on The Dream Team TDT official youtube channel.\r\n\r\n\"Dashain ko Jutta\" was vocal by talented singer/composer Saamba Bal and lyrics by Om K Rai.\r\nMusic Hall Records has arranged the song and we can watch Om K. Rai, Nabin Raj Kunwar, Suban Waiba, Syanboo Tamang acting in the music video. The video was edited and directed by Rabi Lama.\r\n\r\nDashain ko Jutta\r\nON THE ROCKS\r\nVocal/ Compose: Saamba Bal\r\nLyrics: Om K. Rai\r\nArrange: Music Hall Records\r\nDrummer: Anup Dhital\r\nBass: Amar Gurung\r\nLead/Rhythm: Saurab Bhusal\r\nLead/ Rhythm 2: Raju B.K.\r\nArtists: Om K. Rai\r\nNabin Raj Kunwar\r\nSuban Waiba\r\nSyanboo Tamang\r\nDir/Edit: Rabi Lama\r\nCinematography: Suraj Darlami Magar\r\nMUA: Shristi Thapa Magar\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GbbQwSFz2kk\" width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><span data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span></iframe>', 'Dashain Ko Jutta - ON THE ROCKS', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dashain-ko-jutta-on-the-rocks', '', '', '2018-10-14 15:24:15', '2018-10-14 09:39:15', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=3378', 0, 'post', '', 0),
