(3398, 1, '2018-10-15 17:00:29', '2018-10-15 11:15:29', 'The famous rapper Ashish Rana (Laure) will appear on the big screen. He is sure to appear in the lead roll in the movie \'Loure ko Rap\'.\r\nLaurel has played an important role in bringing Nepali rap to the height. Laurel is currently busy on the television reality show \'Roadies\'. After the closing of \'roadies\', he will be busy in this film. Recently the written agreement has been done between Laure and producer Unit.\r\n\r\nZindagi Rocks debut actor, Sonam Pakhrin, has been final along with Laure in the film, and the actress is still remaining to be the finale. Laurel had acted in the movie Tandav in 2014. Which was not commercially successful.\r\n\r\nPasang Yonzan Lama a scriptwriter and director of this movie has been working on its script to the final phase. From falgun, the official team will be going to the floor. In the film, Kasam Nepal will write the script for the movie, choreography by Hari Humagain and the producer will be Dawa Sherpa.\r\n\r\nPasang Yonzan Lama, had directed more than a hundred music videos, this is his debut big budget first movie. According to director Lama, for the first time, the film will publish the story of Raper from the perspective of Nepal. The shooting of the film will take in different places in Kathmandu, Nepal.\r\n\r\nIts Yakha Entertainment Presentation (Dawa Sherpa shetty).\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/lauree-e1539602119331.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3400\" src=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/lauree-e1539602119331.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"932\" height=\"430\" /></a>', 'Laure to star on a mainstream role in the movie \"Laure Ko Rap\"', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'laure-to-star-on-a-mainstream-role-in-the-movie-laure-ko-rap', '', '', '2018-10-16 13:40:52', '2018-10-16 07:55:52', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=3398', 0, 'post', '', 0),
