(3413, 1, '2018-11-04 17:32:38', '2018-11-04 11:47:38', 'My name is Furba Tamang. I am from Dharan the Eastern part of Nepal. I dad finished my SEE in 2074. I was born in 2056/02/14. My first impression and interest towards my musical life from mine childhood.\r\n\r\nMy family background is good. I have got full support from my mom. I got interested in RNB rap songs and I used to sing song among with my friend. And they give good as well as bad commentary for my vocal. But I was focused on my destiny. And I search for opportunity. In this process, I saw the PMST Nepal giving the opportunity to new Artists who are new in the musical industry. We had fix meeting for the project and finally, we completed our first project. Pema Man Singh tamang chairperson of PMST Nepal was a very kind hearted person. Maya launu kunai galti haina is my first project from my pmst Nepal. Thanks you\r\n\r\nFamily details\r\nMother: Shanti Maya Tamang\r\nFather: Birkha Lal Tamang\r\nSister: Pema Tamang\r\n\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IfnZA320XZ0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><span data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span></iframe>', 'Furba Tamang (1st Chance Participant)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'furba-tamang', '', '', '2018-11-04 20:44:28', '2018-11-04 14:59:28', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?post_type=1st_chance&#038;p=3413', 0, '1st_chance', '', 0),
