(3420, 1, '2018-11-12 21:02:07', '2018-11-12 15:17:07', 'The film \'Summer Love\' is based on the famous novel \'Summer Love\' by Subin Bhattari is releasing on Feb 08. The production team has published the main posters of the film featuring Suraj Singh Thakuri, Namrata Sapkota, Ashish Piya and Revati Chhetri.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Final1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-3419\" src=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Final1-711x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"660\" height=\"951\" /></a>\r\n\r\nAshish and Revati are debuting from the movie. While coming back to the movie, Ashish has a background in modeling while Revati is a Miss International winner from India. She has had some experience in acting in India. Revati has already been working in the film like \'Gangs of Northwest\', \'Khatun\', \'Happy Pher Bhag Jayagi\'.\r\n\r\nThe film had directed by Muskan Dhakal. He had earlier directed \'Nai Na Vanula Part 3\'. The film had to work hard to complete the hip of the book. Now we are ready to make the movie as expected to the audience, Dhakal said.\r\n\r\nSubin\'s story has been featured in Samipyaraj Timilsina\'s script, and the film\'s dialogue had written by Subin and Samipyaraj. Khagendra Shrestha and Indra Bhandari are the producers, while Binod Adhikari is executive producers in the film made in Nightingale Entertainment\'s banner.', 'Sharing the Love this Valentine\'s Day \'Summer Love\'', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3417-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-12 21:02:07', '2018-11-12 15:17:07', '', 3417, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/uncategorized/3417-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
