(3426, 1, '2018-11-17 17:30:14', '2018-11-17 11:45:14', 'Shrinkhala Khatiwada was crowned Miss Nepal World 2018 in its 24th edition of the pageant. Shrinkhala Khatiwada of Hetauda overcame 24 other contestants at the grand finale of the beauty pageant in the capital. Khatiwada 22-year-old Khatiwada received the crown from Miss Nepal World 2017 Nikita Chandak at the function.\r\n\r\nShe was born in a small town between the gorgeous mountain of the himalayas and the lost jungles of the terai. Since an early age her mother taught about the truth value of life, about being selfless, about giving to those in need, Despite being an average kid through out her early life she grew up to become the most hardworking student. She studied in the most prestigious engineering college in Nepal and graduated as an architect engineer as a college topper. However 2018 was the turning of her life, she decided to take a challenge contrary, what was expected from her a decision to participate in a beauty pageant. It was an easy for a studious girl who love and limit her self to a comfort of a close group of friends and family to get into glamorous walk and makeups instead of books, research and design. Her core values and root make her confident and now Miss Nepal.\r\n\r\nShrinkhala Khatiwada believes in the power of dream. On here meaning year she got to expore Nepal better than ever the land of 123 ethnic groups, a country that doesn\'t believes in tall buildings but would rather dulled in the Nature. Listening to the stories experiencing the life outside the comfort of the cities she found her self growing someone who she always want to be. Travelling and voluntary works make her realize the impact that she could make shelter, schools, and the hospitals that she could build with all the knowledge she had gain.\r\n\r\nFrom the land of Mount Everest and the birth place of lord Buddha she will represent the unheard voice of shy girls, the strong spirit of our Gorkhas, the strengths of all the independent woman of today, the hardship, resilience and pride of the thirteen million Nepalese and she is so proud to represent this beautiful country of Nepal to wave our flag high at the world stage. She is ready to take any challenge life has to bring. So know she had embarked upon the biggest challenge of her life yet to be miss world 2018.\r\n\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nPt8bK2gbaU\" width=\"100%\" height=\"392\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><span data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span></iframe>', 'Miss Nepal 2018 Shrinkhala Khatiwada representing Nepal in Miss world 2018 (Introduction video)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'miss-nepal-2018-shrinkhala-khatiwada-representing-nepal-in-miss-world-2018-introduction-video', '', '', '2018-11-17 17:31:15', '2018-11-17 11:46:15', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=3426', 0, 'post', '', 0),
