(3470, 1, '2018-12-09 11:51:31', '2018-12-09 06:06:31', 'Releasing on 15 March movie \'Jani Najani\', had released the posters. Manish Shrestha, Nirisha Basnet, Sunny Singh and Namrata Shrestha are the lead artists of the movie on the released poster. Nirisha, the daughter of the old artist and director of Bishow Basnet, is debuting through this movie. Krishna Bhakta Maharjan, Prakash Adhikari and Roshni Kc other artists can be seen in the movie.\n\nSanjay Lama has Cinematographer the movie and music is given by Arjun Pokhrel. Kabiraj Gautraj, Prabin Singh and Shisir Khati have choreography in the movie, and its colorful postal is prepared by Color Blind. Modanath khanal and sagar kaji mali are producers in the Movie .\n\n<a href=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Jani-Najani-Poster.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-3459\" src=\"http://www.pmstnepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Jani-Najani-Poster-711x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"660\" height=\"951\" /></a>', 'Releasing on 15 March movie \'Jani Najani\', had released the posters.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3458-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-09 11:51:31', '2018-12-09 06:06:31', '', 3458, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/uncategorized/3458-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3471, 1, '2018-12-09 23:29:32', '2018-12-09 17:44:32', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After the teaser,  the first original song of the movie ‘Summer Love’ and it’s been titled ‘Saya’. The song includes vocal from Pushpan Pradhan and Banika Pradhan.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<p>As shot in different locations in abroad, this romantic song has featured two major characters of the film: Ashish Piya and Rewati Chettri. Ashish is portraying the role of&nbsp;<em>Atit&nbsp;</em>and Rewati is portraying the role of&nbsp;<em>Saaya,</em>&nbsp;in Summer Love. Now since most of the readers including me have already read the original novel as written by Subin Bhattarai, we’re just looking forward to see how good the film makers have worked to bring the written novel to life.</p>\n\n<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"392\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Z7MsqCUu7b4\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'SAYA - SUMMER LOVE -Nepali Movie Song by Pushpan Pradhan and Banika Pradhan Ft. Ashish Piya and Rewati Chhetri', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'saya-summer-love-nepali-movie-song-by-pushpan-pradhan-and-banika-pradhan-ft-ashish-piya-and-rewati-chhetri', '', '', '2018-12-09 23:32:49', '2018-12-09 17:47:49', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=3471', 0, 'post', '', 0),
