(3543, 1, '2019-01-03 12:27:32', '2019-01-03 06:42:32', 'Sajjan Raj Vaidya, a New York based famous Nepali singer/song writer/guitarist, relesed his another work on youtube this new year. Being highly praised for his work on every single song he has released before, he must have some pressure yet he delivered one of the finest song to kick-start this new year with. With beautifully written lyric, his magical voice and splendid music video,”Hattarindai, battasindai”, will surely make you want to  meet your loved ones or fall in love if you haven’t fallen in love yet. With this gorgeous song he showed us once again what he is capable of.\r\n\r\nThe lyrics of the song is also written by Sajjan himself. The official music video of the song is directed by Nurbu Lama and video features the artists Jonsai Thapa, Arhant Shrestha, Ila Lama &amp; Abhinav Bhatta. Check out the official music video attached below.\r\n\r\n<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"350\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ogr6ygCwRwc\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '\"Haataarindai Bataasindai\" magical voice and splendid music video by Sajjan Raj Vaidya', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'haataarindai-bataasindai-magical-voice-and-splendid-music-video-by-sajjan-raj-vaidya', '', '', '2019-01-03 13:35:06', '2019-01-03 07:50:06', '', 0, 'http://www.pmstnepal.com/?p=3543', 0, 'post', '', 0),
